</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1104000' id='t-1104000'>Now, social organization has reached the global level, and I guess,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1108000' id='t-1108000'>if there's good news I can say I'm bringing you, it's just that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1112000' id='t-1112000'>all the salvation of the world requires is the intelligent pursuit</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1118000' id='t-1118000'>of self-interests in a disciplined and careful way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1124000' id='t-1124000'>It's going to be hard. I say we give it a shot anyway</span>
